e: ￹`Pa~`tapang~`en~ `ita~ `ko~ `wawa~ `ita~.￺We get our children engaged.￻讓我們的孩子訂婚吧！
￹`Tayni~ `to~ `ko~ `tapa~`tapang~ `a~ `tamdaw~.￺Officials have come.￻官方要員已經來了，有頭有臉的人都到齊了
￹`Icowa~ `ko~ `tapang~ `noya~ `sowal~?￺Where did that message come from?￻那信息的根源在哪裡？
￹`Icowa~ `ko~ `ta~`tapangan~ `namo~ `a~ `loma'~?￺Where is your family origin?￻你們出身在那裡？
￹`Satapang~ `sa~`~ `kita~ `anini~ `a~ `ma~`tayal~.￺We start work today.￻我們今天開始工作
